\displaystyle 2x=2r\pi+\frac\pi2-x\iff x=\frac{(4r+1)\pi}6
\displaystyle0\le x\le 2\pi\implies 0\le \frac{(4r+1)\pi}6\le 2\pi\iff 0\le 4r+1\le 12\implies 0\le r\le2
