\displaystyle 2x=(2r+1)\pi-\frac\pi2+x\iff x=\frac{(4r+1)\pi}2
\displaystyle0\le x\le 2\pi\implies 0\le\frac{(4r+1)\pi}2\le 2\pi\implies 0\le(4r+1)\le4\implies r=0
